OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fsunny evening will lead to a largely
OL,7,Fclear night. Patchy mist and cloud
OL,8,Fhowever will form later. A warm night,
OL,9,Fespecially in urban areas. Gentle to
OL,10,Fmoderate easterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,13,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,14,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,15,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,16,FGentle easterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
