OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying dry and settled throughout the
OL,7,Frest of the week and into the weekend.
OL,8,FRemaining very warm initially but
OL,9,Ffeeling a little less warm by Saturday.
